==Writing system==
[[File:Catalan geminated L in a dictionary.jpg|thumb|upright=0.8|The word {{lang|ca|novel·la}} ("novel") in a dictionary. The geminated L ({{lang|ca|l·l}}) is a distinctive character used in Catalan.]]
